@startuml
!theme plain
title Epic 23 - US93: Don Tanino Boss (Scopa)

class DonTaninoBoss {
    - loot_item : ItemString = "Ace"
    + start_scopa_challenge()
    + check_game_result(winner)
    + surrender_loot()
}

class ScopaGame {
    - deck : List<Card>
    - table_cards : List<Card>
    - player_points : int
    - boss_points : int
    + deal_hand()
    + play_card_on_table(card)
    + check_capture_or_scopa()
    + calculate_final_score() : Winner
}

class Player {
    + inventory : List<Item>
    + select_card_from_hand()
    + receive_item(item)
}

' Relazioni
DonTaninoBoss ..> ScopaGame : initiates
ScopaGame --> Player : interacts with
DonTaninoBoss --> Player : gives Ace on Win

note right of DonTaninoBoss::surrender_loot
  Viene chiamato se il 
  giocatore vince la partita
end note

@enduml